review.description: Recently opened under new owner Zack Massey. This place is exactly what a small community needs, fresh fruit and friendly service.  All items are hand picked by the owner and priced well below grocery stores or Walmart. I go here at least 3 times a week and I recommend you do the same.  The owner also supports local schools through fruit donations.  Overall, I highly recommend it.
review.author: Boris P.
